	function Polyvalue = POLY_AT_X(Poly, x)	%	%	Evaluates the value of a polnomial, Poly, with the highest power first, at x 	%	using to Horners method.	%	% Toolbox for ANALOG FILTERS USING MATLAB, Springer, 2009		% Author: 			Lars Wanhammar, 1983-03-15	% Modified by:		LW 2006-01-12, 2007-07-24	%	Copyright:		Divison of Electronics Systems	%					Dept. Electrical Engineering, Linkoping University, Sweden	% Version: 			1	% Known bugs:		None	% Report bugs to:	larsw@isy.liu.se	%		Polyvalue =  0;	for j = 1:length(Poly)		Polyvalue = x*Polyvalue + Poly(j);	end